org.omancode.r.types

Class RDataFrame

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.omancode.r.types.RDataFrame
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CBuilder

    public class RDataFrame
extends Object
implements CBuilder
    An R expression that is an R dataframe. The dataframe "names" attribute is used for the column headings. Implements CBuilder.
    Version:
    $Revision$
    Author:
    Oliver Mannion

           throws RFaceException,

        Create an RDataFrame from an REXP.
        Parameters:
        name - name. If null, one will be generated from the column and row variable names.
        rexp - R expression
        Throws:
        RFaceException - if rexp is not an REXPGenericVector or an R dataframe class.
        UnsupportedTypeException - if rexp contains a type that cannot be handled
